Newspaper! Newspaper!

5
00:01:33,229 --> 00:01:34,750
The new Songjiang Evening Times.

6
00:01:34,750 --> 00:01:35,700
Come get one!

7
00:01:35,990 --> 00:01:37,050
Newspaper! Newspaper!

8
00:01:37,050 --> 00:01:37,530
