9
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,620
I would like a copy.

10
00:01:40,190 --> 00:01:40,750
Here.

11
00:01:44,350 --> 00:01:46,150
Sir, I don't have enough change.

12
00:01:47,470 --> 00:01:48,400
Keep the change.

13
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,410
Do something for me.

14
00:01:51,430 --> 00:01:52,660
Go to Minyi Street

15
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,300
at 7 a.m. tomorrow.

16
00:01:54,770 --> 00:01:55,910
Be early rather than late.

17
00:01:55,910 --> 00:01:57,150
Shout a couple of lines for me.

18
00:01:57,150 --> 00:01:57,810
Shout what?

19
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:02,920
Whatever the twisted doughnut seller shouts, you shout too.

20
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,510
Okay.

21
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:08,070
Newspaper! Newspaper!

22
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:09,930
The new Songjiang Evening Times.

23
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,870
Two more dishes and we're all set.

24
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:24,910
Don't wait for Aunt Chang and I.

25
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:25,690
You eat first.

26
00:02:25,690 --> 00:02:28,290
Otherwise, it'll smell fishy once it's stale.

27
00:02:28,329 --> 00:02:29,930
Take a cup and drink with me.

28
00:02:33,950 --> 00:02:35,750
I haven't seen you drink at home.

29
00:02:36,060 --> 00:02:37,460
Is there something good?

30
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,590
I can't say what's up,

31
00:02:40,230 --> 00:02:41,490
but it's no doubt good.

32
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,579
I caught the person I wanted,

33
00:02:44,579 --> 00:02:45,380
does that count?

34
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,300
Of course.

35
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:56,150
Can you drink when you have gastric issues?

36
00:02:57,270 --> 00:02:58,590
Whether it hurts or not

37
00:02:58,930 --> 00:03:00,040
depends on my mood.

38
00:03:08,810 --> 00:03:10,670
Does that gastric medicine work?

39
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:20,290
When did you buy that medicine?

40
00:03:20,290 --> 00:03:23,550
I've never heard you say you have stomach problems before.

41
00:03:26,570 --> 00:03:27,370
Last Tuesday.

42
00:03:27,970 --> 00:03:30,370
So you were in a bad mood since last Tuesday?

43
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:40,510
Then you should come back and rest after you've bought the medicine.

44
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,020
I came back early that day.

45
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:47,079
You see, if you came back, I could still take care of you.

46
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:50,920
Where have you been all day with your stomachache?

47
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:52,780
Why are you talking so much today?

48
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:54,480
And you're fast.

49
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:57,630
I haven't heard the first sentence clearly,

50
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:59,490
and then the second line follows.

51
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,360
Don't just drink.

52
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:02,950
Eat.

53
00:04:05,070 --> 00:04:06,670
It's all because of the wine.

54
00:04:07,290 --> 00:04:08,630
It's... It's also my first time

55
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:10,080
drinking this.

56
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,070
I didn't hold back

57
00:04:11,070 --> 00:04:12,190
and scolded you.

58
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:14,090
I won't drink anymore.

59
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:16,870
Here's the soup.

60
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,760
Sir, drink it while it's hot.

61
00:04:27,230 --> 00:04:28,110
You are done?

62
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:29,620
I'm full.

63
00:04:41,050 --> 00:04:42,130
What did I say?

64
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,780
What I did the other day

65
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:01,660
was inappropriate.

66
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:03,290
Hu Bin, I've told you.

67
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:05,170
We'll talk about business back in the department.

68
00:05:05,170 --> 00:05:07,570
We'll talk about everything else outside.

69
00:05:08,470 --> 00:05:09,570
Anything else?

70
00:05:11,990 --> 00:05:12,710
Is there anything to eat?

71
00:05:12,710 --> 00:05:14,170
-I haven’t eaten yet.
-No.

72
00:05:18,590 --> 00:05:19,780
I'm just cheap.

73
00:05:20,610 --> 00:05:21,790
Regardless of how you treat me,

74
00:05:21,790 --> 00:05:23,280
I have to apologize to you.

75
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:24,450
I know last time...

76
00:05:26,990 --> 00:05:27,940
Forget about last time.

77
00:05:27,940 --> 00:05:28,780
It's in the past.

78
00:05:28,780 --> 00:05:29,580
Let's move on.

79
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:32,280
Even if you don't like me,

80
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:34,010
can we not hold grudges?

81
00:05:34,150 --> 00:05:35,030
Just like how we were before,

82
00:05:35,030 --> 00:05:36,960
-let's keep up the banter.
-Hu Bin.

83
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,690
I've got a lawsuit on my hands now.

84
00:05:40,190 --> 00:05:42,870
Even a dog should know how to judge people.

85
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:45,070
Do you think I'm in the mood

86
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,360
to listen to you whine?

87
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,610
Move.

88
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:57,500
Don't talk.

89
00:05:57,909 --> 00:05:58,840
Don't follow me.

